  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210700/extras/39872e557467e2822b1f251f8338e4ee.avif?t=1689292795\" width=600 height=300 /></span><br>In the early 20th century, the citizens of a vanished country started to fight. And at the center of it all is the young man ‘ Pyotr', who has chosen no nation.<br><br>Experience a story set against real history and become the protagonist yourself!<br>You can experience a sad story that unfolds amidst the tragic history of war.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Immersive Story</strong></h2>\"Pechka\" is a story centered around the journey of the young man 'Pyotr' and the struggles and conflicts of the vanished country's citizens. Immerse yourself in the drama unfolding amidst the tragic history of war.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210700/extras/1d67dbb98caf869b16b40a83310bc817.poster.avif?t=1689292795\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210700/extras/1d67dbb98caf869b16b40a83310bc817.webm?t=1689292795\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210700/extras/1d67dbb98caf869b16b40a83310bc817.mp4?t=1689292795\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Meticulously Verified Historical Facts and Authentic Sources</strong></h2>From World War I to the Bolshevik Revolution to Korea's independence movement, the game is set in the Russian Far East in the early 20th century, offering a thorough historical and period authenticity to provide players with a realistic experience.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210700/extras/55f01d90a103761b1f7889842bb58dbe.poster.avif?t=1689292795\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210700/extras/55f01d90a103761b1f7889842bb58dbe.webm?t=1689292795\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210700/extras/55f01d90a103761b1f7889842bb58dbe.mp4?t=1689292795\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210700/extras/d031c7bbf82e0deb2ed20fb9d6487e41.poster.avif?t=1689292795\" width=600 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210700/extras/d031c7bbf82e0deb2ed20fb9d6487e41.webm?t=1689292795\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210700/extras/d031c7bbf82e0deb2ed20fb9d6487e41.mp4?t=1689292795\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Betrayal, Death, and Love</strong></h2>\"Pechka\" explores various emotions and themes such as betrayal, death, and love. Through this, players will empathize with the choices and struggles of the characters as they experience a range of emotions throughout the story.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210700/extras/3c56fc51866e4d0001dab69323698d0e.poster.avif?t=1689292795\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210700/extras/3c56fc51866e4d0001dab69323698d0e.webm?t=1689292795\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210700/extras/3c56fc51866e4d0001dab69323698d0e.mp4?t=1689292795\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Intimacy System and Multiple Endings</strong></h2>Pay close attention to the intimacy levels with the characters, which change based on the player's choices and actions. These interactions will lead to various endings. Discover the impact of this era's tragedy through your own choices.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210700/extras/f35282957524ed157c837a251cc8b915.poster.avif?t=1689292795\" width=600 height=358 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210700/extras/f35282957524ed157c837a251cc8b915.webm?t=1689292795\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210700/extras/f35282957524ed157c837a251cc8b915.mp4?t=1689292795\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Small Stories</strong></h2>The game progresses by unraveling small stories that contribute to the completion of the overall narrative. Players immerse themselves in this turbulent era by exploring and making choices within these tales.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210700/extras/3d6611d412bbf19deded6aaa115d40d0.poster.avif?t=1689292795\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210700/extras/3d6611d412bbf19deded6aaa115d40d0.webm?t=1689292795\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210700/extras/3d6611d412bbf19deded6aaa115d40d0.mp4?t=1689292795\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Adorable Cats</strong></h2>Cute cats make appearances in the game, adding joy to the gaming world.<br>Discover various cats that appear throughout the game.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210700/extras/65b6c623d801ac728f9747a2facfa37b.poster.avif?t=1689292795\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210700/extras/65b6c623d801ac728f9747a2facfa37b.webm?t=1689292795\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210700/extras/65b6c623d801ac728f9747a2facfa37b.mp4?t=1689292795\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
